snippet.textDisplay: Let me start by saying that I am a big fan of Kenny Rogers'. He was my favorite country singer. That being said, He was not a very nice person to his fans. Every account I have seen where he was approached and asked for an autograph or a picture, he obliged, but he would treat the fans like they were just peppercorns in a grinder. All the same and going to the same place. My sister-in-law experienced this first hand when she went to one of his concerts. I think he was getting tired of the spotlight.
